Weather condition glyphs (plan 082)
===================================

The SVG files in this directory (clear-day.svg, clear-night.svg,
extreme-rain.svg, fog.svg, hail.svg, overcast.svg,
partly-cloudy-day.svg, partly-cloudy-night.svg, rain.svg, snow.svg,
thunderstorms.svg, wind.svg) are static-fill exports of Meteocons,
by Bas Milius.

License: MIT
Upstream: https://github.com/basmilius/weather-icons

These are vendored byte-identical copies of the same files at
prototype/assets/weather/ (that directory documents the original
gallery pairing this app's condition→art table implements). No
modification, "optimization", or re-export has been applied to
either copy — the provenance stays traceable file-for-file.

Of the 12 files, 10 are actively assigned to a condition in
src/lib/weatherArt.ts. `extreme-rain.svg`, `wind.svg`, and
`hail.svg` are vendored but unassigned — spare buckets for a future
condition mapping, exactly as in the prototype gallery.
